{"word":"ἀχανής","slug":"ἀχανής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀχανής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>χανεῖν</el>, aor2 <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> of <a href='S:χάσκω'><el>χάσκω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>not opening the mouth</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(<el>α</el> <a href='S:euphonic'>euphon.</a> ) <i>yawning, wide</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}